See build/README.md for build instructions.

 Note that the software in this directory is primarily licensed under the GNU General Public License, version 2 (see COPYING), 
 as are the modifications applied in build/0001-Xilinx-NGcodec-hevc-ffmpeg-plugin.patch.

 The build process pulls unmodified source files for the following packages from the following URLs:

 * NASM 2.13.01 - http://www.nasm.us/pub/nasm/releasebuilds/2.13.01/nasm-2.13.01.tar.gz
 * YASM 1.3.0 - http://www.tortall.net/projects/yasm/releases/yasm-1.3.0.tar.gz
 * libx265 - hg clone https://bitbucket.org/multicoreware/x265
 * ffmpeg 3.3 - git clone https://git.ffmpeg.org/ffmpeg.git ffmpeg -b release/3.3

 Additionally the software in this directory includes a build/CL/ subdirectory with MIT-licensed 
 OpenCL Headers from The Khronos Group Inc.
